WEBVTT

00:00:06.529 --> 00:00:08.750
Za mnoge je ena izmed najbolj kul stvari

00:00:08.750 --> 00:00:09.804
pri "Igri prestolov",

00:00:09.804 --> 00:00:12.221
da imajo prebivalci Dothraškega morja

00:00:12.221 --> 00:00:14.244
svoj lastni pravi jezik.

00:00:14.244 --> 00:00:16.288
In Dothraki so sledili

00:00:16.288 --> 00:00:20.168
pravemu jeziku, ki ga Na'vi
govorijo v "Avatarju",

00:00:20.168 --> 00:00:21.805
ki so ga, zagotovo, Na'vi potrebovali,

00:00:21.805 --> 00:00:23.377
ker so Klingoni v "Star Treku"

00:00:23.377 --> 00:00:24.892
imeli svoj lasten jezik

00:00:24.892 --> 00:00:26.802
že od 1979.

00:00:26.802 --> 00:00:28.858
In ne pozabimo na vilinske jezike

00:00:28.858 --> 00:00:32.188
v trilogiji "Gospodar prstanov"
J. R. R. Tolkiena,